C)\n	Bangalore Centre for Internet & Society\n','2015-01-22 15:04:33'),(64,'stopbadware','\nBerkman Center established the non-profit organization StopBadware, which aims to stop viruses, spyware, and other threats to the open Internet\nStopBadware became an independent entity supported by Google, PayPal, Mozilla, and Nominum','2015-01-22 15:07:13'),(66,'#5 #copybook','\nnalaiko tam_@haja andrwn\n\nmanagement\nia: intelligence artificielle\nodia: outil de dev pour ia\nmicrocontroleur\ncompta\nid: info_decisionnelle\n','2015-01-24 15:44:02'),(68,'#hormone#cortisole','\nIts functions are to increase blood sugar\nto aid the metabolism of fat, protein, \nto decrease bone formation\nactivates anti-stress and anti-inflammatory pathways.\nprevents the release of substances in the body that cause inflammation\n','2015-01-25 04:28:27'),(69,'dad marar','ourn n cabln oon :D','2015-01-25 06:09:12'),(70,'dad marar','angalana batsena oon i tiantsoa\nnery aa, nery aaa,....... mba mafy loha koa ani zany olona k','2015-01-25 06:14:56'),(71,'#movie to,watch #fiction','lucy','2015-01-30 23:19:18'),(72,'#movie to,watch #fiction','transcendance','2015-01-30 23:19:26'),(73,'#metal #group','\nthe degree of the music will be measured from 0 to 10\nfleshgod apocalypse					9\ncradle of filth						9\nmetallica							5\n','2015-01-31 19:34:05'),(74,'#movie ,to,watch ,gasy','malagasy mankany','2015-02-02 12:33:53'),(75,'from movie lucy','the drug is called:cph4\n\nfemme enceinte fabrique cph4 durant grossesse a une quantite tres pti\ndurant 6em mois du grossesse\nqui fait en sorte que foetus forme tous les os du corps du bebe\n\nher friend got a pbm then,\nshe had to:\n	follow the instructions that lucy gave her\n	do sports\n	eat normally\n','2015-02-02 13:13:33'),(76,'#5 -schedule','\n                                                \n                 mon   |  thu  |  wed    |thr  | fri   | sat\n                -------+-------+---------+-----+-------+----------\n                 mgt   |  id   |  compta |     | gsm   | sgbdr\n                 gp    |  eco  |  odia   |     | telec | coo\n                 mcp   |  uml  |         | ro  | eco   |\n                 eng   |  elec |         | gafi| microc|\n','2015-02-05 15:34:50'),(77,'#general_culture -korea #movie-interview','\nkorea-north is now led by #kim-jong-oon\nit is not with the usa\nit is the south of korea which is with the usa\n\nthe qg of cia is in langley-virginie\n\nkim-jong-oon works a lot so he doesn_t pee and poo at all :D\nhe has not an asshole :D\njames_franco, seth_rogen','2015-02-06 21:53:31'),(78,'#cook -ls','misao\nlegume sy henakisoa\nanana sy henakisoa','2015-02-07 14:33:09'),(79,'#cook -simple-spaghetti','\nIngredients:\n===================================================\nDried spaghetti\nRed sauce (vodka sauce, marinara, etc.)\nGrated parmesan cheese (optional)\nButter or olive oil (optional)\n\n1:	Fill a medium sized pot with cold water. Place it on the stove on high heat. Bring to a boil. \n2:	break the spaghetti in half\n	Carefully place the spaghetti into the boiling water, \n		making sure the spaghetti is completely covered with water.\n	reduce the heat so it doesn\'t boil over\n	stirring the pasta lightly\n3:	Cook for 7-15 minutes, depending on your preference,\n	Spaghetti should be soft in the center but not mushy\n		If the center is still hard, allow to cook for an additional minute\n4:	remove pot from heat.\n	drain the pasta using a colander or strainer\n\n5:	preparing the sauce\n	Pour sauce into a small pan\n	Place the pan on the stove on high heat, and bring to a boil. \n	Reduce to a simmer\n	Allow to cook for up to 20 minutes,\n	stir occasionally\n6: remove from heat\n	Allow the sauce to cool for a few minutes\n	serve the sauce on top of the pasta\n\n7:	place a frying pan on the stove on high heat\n	Cut a piece of butter(about 1/2inch thick for one serving)\n	put the butter on the stove\n	allow the butter to melt\n	Drizzle the butter on top of the pasta.\n\nServe and enjoy\n	Add grated basil, parmesan cheese, for extra flavor\n','2015-02-07 15:10:27'),(80,'fried-pasta-with-veggies #cook','\ningedients:\n=====================================================\n8 ounces spaghetti\n2 cloves crushed garlic \n2 tablespoons olive oil\n1 onion, sliced into thin rings\n2 skinless, boneless chicken breast halves - cut into bite-size pieces\n2 cups broccoli florets\n2 cups cauliflower florets\n2 cups julienned carrots\nsalt to taste\nground black pepper to taste\n2 tablespoons soy sauce\n\n\n\n\nREADY IN\n45 mins\n\nPREP\n20 mins\n\nCOOK\n25 mins\n\n\n\n\ndirections:\n======================================================\n1:	Bring a large pot of water to a boil\n	Cook spaghetti pasta in boiling water until al dente.\n	Drain\nMeanwhile,\n	heat oil in a large skillet over medium-high heat\n	Cook garlic in oil for 1 minute\n	Stir in onion, and cook until soft\n	Stir in chicken\n	Mix in the broccoli, cauliflower, and carrots, \n		and cook for 2 to 5 minutes\n	stir it frequently\n	Season with soy sauce, salt, and pepper.\n\ntoss pasta with vegies\n\nserve warm\n','2015-02-07 15:51:06');
